        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "買いたいけど、お金がないんだ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "行きたいんだけど、都合がつかないんだ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "やりたいことはある、だって、まだ諦めたくないんだ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 3,
        "gloss": "even",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "彼は、自分より年下の子にだって、馬鹿にされている。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "こんな簡単な問題でさえ、彼は解けないんだ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "どんなに忙しくても、家族との時間は大切にしたい。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 4,
        "gloss": "too",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "私も、その映画を見たいと思っていたんだ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "彼も、コンサートに行くらしいよ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "このケーキ、美味しいね！私も好きだ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 5,
        "gloss": "they say",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "あの店は、すごく美味しいらしいよ、だって、友達が言ってた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "来週、雨が降るらしいよ、だって、天気予報で言ってた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "彼は、もうすぐ海外に行くらしい、だって、噂になってる。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            }
          ],
